ill attempt to place\ninto a much broader context the unimodality of the posets $M(n)$ of staircase\npartitions, for which determining a combinatorial proof remains an outstanding\nopen problem.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 27 May 2013 00:44:13 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 8 Jul 2013 09:25:00 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Sat, 21 Mar 2015 23:34:40 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-11-10"}
